n0=;Safety And Security On IRC Enabling Script By Khaled Mardem Bay  (Endorsed And Approved By #Nohack IRC.Dal.Net)
n1=;
n2=;Official IRC Safety And Protection Script
n3=;
n4=;Must Remain Loaded To Stop IRC Exploitation By Malicious Users And Trojan Port Scanning.
n5=;
n6=;Complete Protection Against All Currently Known Trojans And IRC Exploits And Backdoors.
n7=;
n8=;Please Remember It Is Potentially Dangerous To Accept Files From Users You Do Not Know On IRC
n9=:
n10=:Accepting And Running Files From Other Users Could Put You At Risk Of Virus Infection.
n11=;
n12=;Tested By :- Fuggs & Raistwork [ Dal.Net IRC Operators ]  RichG & awni [ #nohack channel operators ] 
n13=;
n14=;If you want privacy in the electronic age, you have to give it to yourself.
n15=;Your employer will not give it to you. Your government will not give it to you.
n16=;Even the laws of your nation cannot be relied upon to give it to you. There's a
n17=;saying that freedom of the press belongs to those who own one. Privacy also
n18=;belongs to those who create it for themselves. To give yourself privacy in
n19=;electronic communications, you need to understand the basic knowledge of
n20=;hackers tactics and protect your personal data from these techno age
n21=;criminals and exploiters. Let's make IRC a nicer place to chat and have fun.
